fPriorPredictive <- function(numSamples, a, b, N){
  lX <- vector(length = numSamples)
  for(i in 1:numSamples){
    theta <- rbeta(n = 1, shape1 = a, shape2 = b)
    lX[i] <- rbinom(n = 1, size = N, prob = theta )
    #cat("\n\n theta: ", theta)
    #cat("\n lX[i] : ", lX[i])
  }
  
  return(lX)
}

lX <- fPriorPredictive(1000, 1, 1, 100)
cat("\n Mean: ", mean(lX))
